description: Gets the operation result of operation triggered by Export Jobs API. If the operation is successful, then it alsocontains URL of a Blob and a SAS key to access the same. The blob contains exported jobs in JSON serialized format.

vault_name.description: The name of the recovery services vault.

resource_group_name.description: The name of the resource group where the recovery services vault is present.

operation_id.description: OperationID which represents the export job.

statuscode.description: HTTP Status Code of the operation.

headers.description: HTTP headers associated with this operation.
